      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CYCLONE TIM (1) has mixed form, but did hit the frame three back and was narrowly beaten next start before a fourth (19.22) at this track in a Restricted WIN latest. Likely to improve sharply this time. BROTHER SAM (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (19.98) last time in a Grade 5 at Capalaba. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. Expected to give a good account. TSUNAMI SEA (2) pinged the lids and was in the firing line throughout but drifted out of it when 6th at this track in a Grade 5. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Can measure up this time. FASCINATE MARK (3) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
